column5: Greetings,Who is going to the All Canada Show this weekend in Green Bay, WI? If so, what might you be looking for? Sunday might be very quiet given that the Packers are playing in the early game.Good fishing and tight lines!!
I think we're probably in trouble for the Sunday crowd, but that just means Friday and Saturday will be that much better! We really enjoy Green Bay. Hope to meet some of you there!
